IronSource Opt-Out
Opt-Out:
mobile-gdpr-requests@ironsrc.com
Submit a request to
mobile-gdpr-requests@ironsrc.com
containing a proof of your personal IDFA/GAID. Please mention in the subject line if it is a deletion or pull request.
    ironSource will process the request within 30 days, subject to our GDPR policy
    For access requests, we will reply with data covering the categories included in the linked excel templates
    For deletion requests, we will send a confirmation email which confirms that your IDFA/GAID was deleted
